summary: 21-Day Smoke Inhalation Study with 20,000 Cigarette smokers in Switzerland. The results were published in the Journal of the Swiss Academy of Sciences and Humanities (JSAH) on Nov. 25, 2013. Study was part of a larger study into the effects of smoke inhalation on blood lymphocytes.
